name: Guardian Canadian Sector Controlled Equity Fund
longDescription: Guardian Canadian Sector Controlled Equity Fund seeks to achieve long-term growth of capita In order to achieve its investment objectives, the Guardian Canadian Sector Controlled Equity Fund invests, directly or indirectly, primarily in common shares or other equity-related securities issued by Canadian companies with a focus on reducing exposure to resources.
